			div(data-book='licenseImage', lang='*') license.png?1385485792397
			div(data-book='licenseUrl', lang='*') http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/
			div(data-book='licenseDescription', lang='en') You may not use this work for commercial purposes. You may not alter, transform, or build upon this work without permission. You must attribute the work in the manner specified by the author.
		.bloom-page.cover.coverColor.bloom-frontMatter.A5Portrait(data-export='front-matter-cover', data-page='required singleton',
				id='8420c464-ce0f-4b23-8132-87f526cda9bf')
			.pageLabel(lang='en') Front Cover
			.marginBox
				.bloom-translationGroup.coverTitle
